Reader.Name: tab_detail_financing_factLoad
Reader.Sql:
select DISTINCT B.projectName, B.guarantyOrgID, B.hostAreaID, B.oprationCompany, B.attribution, A.reportDate, A.fullBankCode, A.loadEndDate, c.relationMain, IFNULL(A.loadSum,0) AS loadSum, IFNULL(IFNULL(B.mustServiceSum,0)-IFNULL(B.factServiceSum,0),0) as mustServiceSum, A.fullBankCode, (SELECT IFNULL(SUM(IFNULL(projCost.mustCostSum,0)-IFNULL(projCost.factCostSum,0)),0) FROM pro_projCost projCost where projCost.project_ID = B.project_ID and projCost.costType='01' ${has(begindatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate>='"+begindatesql+"'"):""} ${has(enddatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate<='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} )as mustGuaraCostSum, (SELECT IFNULL(SUM(IFNULL(projCost.mustCostSum,0)-IFNULL(projCost.factCostSum,0)),0) FROM pro_projCost projCost where projCost.project_ID = B.project_ID and projCost.costType='05' ${has(begindatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate>='"+begindatesql+"'"):""} ${has(enddatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate<='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} )as mustReviewCostSum, projCost.factCostDate, B.aManID, B.bManID from pro_factload A LEFT JOIN pro_project B ON A.projectID = B.project_ID LEFT JOIN pro_projCost projCost ON projCost.project_ID = B.project_ID LEFT JOIN crm_client c ON c.client_ID=B.clientID WHERE A.busiTypeID='01'
${has(begindatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate>='"+begindatesql+"'"):""} ${has(enddatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate<='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} order by projCost.factCostDate
Reader.Description:
select DISTINCT B.projectName, B.guarantyOrgID, B.hostAreaID, B.oprationCompany, B.attribution, A.reportDate, A.fullBankCode, A.loadEndDate, c.relationMain, IFNULL(A.loadSum,0) AS loadSum, IFNULL(IFNULL(B.mustServiceSum,0)-IFNULL(B.factServiceSum,0),0) as mustServiceSum, A.fullBankCode, (SELECT IFNULL(SUM(IFNULL(projCost.mustCostSum,0)-IFNULL(projCost.factCostSum,0)),0) FROM pro_projCost projCost where projCost.project_ID = B.project_ID and projCost.costType='01' ${has(begindatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate>='"+begindatesql+"'"):""} ${has(enddatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate<='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} )as mustGuaraCostSum, (SELECT IFNULL(SUM(IFNULL(projCost.mustCostSum,0)-IFNULL(projCost.factCostSum,0)),0) FROM pro_projCost projCost where projCost.project_ID = B.project_ID and projCost.costType='05' ${has(begindatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate>='"+begindatesql+"'"):""} ${has(enddatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate<='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} )as mustReviewCostSum, projCost.factCostDate, B.aManID, B.bManID from pro_factload A LEFT JOIN pro_project B ON A.projectID = B.project_ID LEFT JOIN pro_projCost projCost ON projCost.project_ID = B.project_ID LEFT JOIN crm_client c ON c.client_ID=B.clientID WHERE A.busiTypeID='01'
${has(begindatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate>='"+begindatesql+"'"):""} ${has(enddatesql)?(" and projCost.factCostDate<='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} order by projCost.factCostDate
